Typography should feel:
- luxury
- bold but controlled
- cinematic
- editorial
- modern
- visually confident

Preferred typography behaviour:
- mixed hierarchy
- oversized focal wording
- refined supporting text
- layered type interaction
- controlled spacing
- strong alignment systems
